sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>Configurable HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant Milvus as Milvus<br/>Configurable HTTP/gRPC
    participant vLLMEmb as vLLM Embedding<br/>Configurable HTTP/HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMEval as LMEval Job
    participant FMS as TrustyAI FMS<br/>Configurable HTTP/HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,PG: Flow 1: Inference Request (vLLM Backend)
        Client->>LLS: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/8321 (no app auth)
        LLS->>vLLM: Forward inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (VLLM_TLS_VERIFY)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (VLLM_API_TOKEN)
        vLLM-->>LLS: Inference response
        LLS->>PG: Store inference log (async)<br/>PostgreSQL/5432<br/>Auth: username/password
        LLS-->>Client: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,vLLMEmb: Flow 2: RAG Query with Vector Search
        Client->>LLS: POST /v1/vector-io/query<br/>HTTP/8321
        LLS->>Milvus: Vector similarity search<br/>HTTP/gRPC (configurable mTLS)<br/>Auth: Token (MILVUS_TOKEN)
        Milvus-->>LLS: Matching vectors
        LLS->>vLLMEmb: Generate embedding<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (configurable)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        vLLMEmb-->>LLS: Embedding vector
        LLS->>vLLM: Inference with context<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (VLLM_API_TOKEN)
        vLLM-->>LLS: Augmented response
        LLS->>PG: Store conversation state<br/>PostgreSQL/5432
        LLS-->>Client: RAG Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,LMEval: Flow 3: Model Evaluation (TrustyAI LMEval)
        Client->>LLS: POST /v1/eval/run<br/>HTTP/8321
        LLS->>K8sAPI: Create LMEval Job<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>LLS: Job created
        LMEval->>vLLM: Evaluate model<br/>HTTP (configurable)
        vLLM-->>LMEval: Evaluation results
        LLS-->>Client: Evaluation status
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over Client,FMS: Flow 4: Safety Shield Evaluation
        Client->>LLS: POST /v1/safety/run_shield<br/>HTTP/8321
        LLS->>FMS: Evaluate content safety<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (FMS_SSL_CERT_PATH)<br/>Auth: None
        FMS-->>LLS: Shield evaluation result
        LLS-->>Client: Safety response
    end
